&lt;h1 id="the-hardest-lessons-for-startups-to-learn"&gt;The Hardest Lessons for Startups to Learn&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;April 2006&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(This essay is derived from a talk at the 2006 Startup School.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The startups we&amp;rsquo;ve funded so far are pretty quick, but they seem quicker to learn some lessons than others. I think it&amp;rsquo;s because some things about startups are kind of counterintuitive.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>